This utility provides various ways of syncing song rating tag metadata to various other formats.

What you'll need to get started (ubuntu package names):

$ sudo apt-get install build-essential cmake libtag1-dev

Optional:

$ sudo apt-get install libmpdclient-dev

Example initial build (after prerequisites are installed):

$ mkdir ratesync; cd ratesync
ratesync$ git init
ratesync$ git pull git://github.com/nickbp/ratesync.git
ratesync$ mkdir bin; cd bin
ratesync/bin$ cmake ../src  (generates makefiles)
ratesync/bin$ make
ratesync/bin$ ./ratesync

All set! You can configure the build using ccmake or cmake-gui.
